      <title>由于销售增长放缓，全球基金出售联合利华印度股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/foreign-holding-in-hindustan-unilever-drops-to-four-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于印度斯坦联合利华有限公司 (Hindustan Unilever Ltd.) 面临消费者需求疲软和竞争加剧的局面，全球投资者已将其持股量降至四年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/foreign-holding-in-hindustan-unilever-drops-to-four-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院向拜登发送包括伊朗石油制裁在内的一揽子援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/senate-sends-aid-package-with-iran-oil-sanctions-to-biden-s-desk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院投票决定向总统乔·拜登发送一项外国援助计划，其中包括对伊朗石油部门的制裁，拜登表示他将签署该法案成为法律。]]></description>
